magic phase

name:	click on a self/friendly character/unit
actor:	phasing player
goal:	Basic Game Operation
preconditions:	In the phase that player can act
summary:
steps:
		1. Player select and click on a character/unit
		2. Computer display all the information for that unit in the info dialog on the side of the window
		3. Computer also display a dialog with following buttoms based on the phase the player is taking
			a. Move
			b. Cast spell
alternative:
postcondition:

